<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf1c31b4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s10261"><num value="10261">§ 10261.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in this subchapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbf1c31b5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s10261/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> The term “Chairman” means the Chairman of the Nuclear Waste Technical Review Board.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbf1c31b6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s10261/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> The term “Board” means the Nuclear Waste Technical Review Board established under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s10262">section 10262 of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idbf1c31b7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/425/tV/s501">Pub. L. 97–425, title V, § 501</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/100/202/s101/d/tIII">Pub. L. 100–202, § 101(d) [title III]</ref>, <date date="1987-12-22">Dec. 22, 1987</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/101/1329-104">101 Stat. 1329–104</ref>, 1329–121; <ref href="/us/pl/100/203/tV/s5051">Pub. L. 100–203, title V, § 5051</ref>, <date date="1987-12-22">Dec. 22, 1987</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/101/1330-248">101 Stat. 1330–248</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
